Main Projects
1. Thomson Reuters Regulatory News Integration

Situation: Within the Convergence Risk framework, the team aimed to accelerate and automate the processing of regulatory news feeds from Thomson Reuters.

Task: Lead the integration of regulatory data sources and explore the use of LLMs to enhance content interpretation.

Action: Designed and optimized ingestion and classification flows, implemented LLM-based text analysis modules, and aligned results with business and compliance expectations.

Result: Delivered a 30% improvement in processing speed and strengthened the accuracy and reliability of regulatory news analysis.

2. Verbatim Analysis ‚Äì HR Project

Situation: HR and compliance teams needed faster, deeper insights from qualitative feedback.

Task: Build a semantic analysis pipeline for open-text responses to extract key risk and engagement indicators.

Action: Developed and implemented transformer-based NLP models, streamlined preprocessing, and collaborated with business stakeholders for validation and adoption.

Result: Achieved a ~30% acceleration in analytics turnaround, enabling HR and Compliance to respond faster to employee insights.

